
Error[E-L_ESC_BLOCK]: Pointer value to stack escapes the lifetime of its block
at compile/lang_tests/lifetimes/stack/stack_nesting.rna:6:17:6:22
  :         outer = inner;
  :                 ^^^^^ Escape occurs here
  :
  : Conflicting lifetime requirements:
  : 1. Lifetime '*stack' may not outlive '*stack'
  : 2. Lifetime '*stack' must outlive '*stack'
  .
 ... caused by 1.
  -> 'int*stack' assigned to pointer with lifetime '*stack'
  :
 == note: pointee 'int' is lifetime-permissive, its lifetime may be shortened.
  .
 ... caused by 2.
  -> '*stack<outer>' lifetime is greater than '*stack<inner>'
  :
 == note: involving '*stack' lifetime for this inner block
  :     {
  :     ^  --- stack_nesting.rna:3:5


